# Age Verification Plugin

## Description
The Age Verification Plugin is designed to restrict access to your website based on the user's age. This plugin prompts users to verify their age before accessing the content, ensuring compliance with age-related regulations.

## Installation
1. Download the plugin package.
2. Extract the contents to the `/plugins/nielsvandendries/ageverification` directory of your website.
3. Activate the plugin from the plugins management page in your website's admin panel.

## Usage
1. After activation, navigate to the layout and add the component.
2. Configure the age verification settings according to your requirements in the component.
3. Save the settings and the age verification prompt will be enabled on your website.

## Features
- Customizable age verification prompt
- Option to set minimum age requirement
- Configurable appearance and text of the verification prompt
- Option to remember user's age verification status

